==English==
===Etymology===
From the past participle stem of Latin ''nictitare'', frequentative form of ''nictare'' ‘wink’ (see [[nictate]]).

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /'nɪktɪteɪtɪŋ/

===Adjective===
{{en-ad|nictitating}}
# [[winking]], [[blinking]]

===Verb===
'''nictitating'''
* present participle of [[nictitate]]